review.reviewBody: Flavourful food, nice sized portions, arrived hot, well packaged. Rice and potatoes were both very good. Lamb was tender. Moussaka was quite tasty, thank you.
First time trying this place. 8 oz New York Steak Dinner was really good...
This restaurant is a complete hit or a complete disaster to the point of throwing it all out. $100 in the toilet today.
